{"tid":802861,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我做緊份pt番滿左兩個月係咪應該有有薪病假","createTime":"2018-09-01T18:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T18:39:10.000Z","uid":165071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce30d9202aa99cb1c23367af5b5fed5c886f957a","tid":802861,"uid":165071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟做緊一份pt<br />\n由6月底做起<br />\n我每個星期都番5.5日(44小時）番到8月31號<br />\n符合左勞工法例既418<br />\n我每個月請左兩日sl 都有醫生紙 係咪應該<br />\n可以追番果4日sl?"},{"pid":"f91e7176192169cafc913beb3c8bf1ff2fc46cda","tid":802861,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"36bb64f79dbe2c00cc2d7d535062ffacddca0ee0","tid":802861,"uid":165071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f91e7176192169cafc913beb3c8bf1ff2fc46cda","tid":802861,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"可以"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:25:36.000Z","msg":"岩先打左去勞工處問 佢話無"},{"pid":"44ebd23841d046d7c151cf5edb80304bd94d3031","tid":802861,"uid":47546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:27:31.000Z","msg":"連續4星期個個星期超過先有"},{"pid":"0ca91b8cec060a2316712e7a140aca526261a69a","tid":802861,"uid":66380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:32:54.000Z","msg":"除左要有草夠sick leave，病假要醫生開4天或以上嗰啲先算。一兩日sick leave代表小事，係唔受勞工法例保障。香港勞工法例係保障商家唔係勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3896d9a1fadddf84ef453a6404fe936a6858cd71","tid":802861,"uid":132047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"放心係無既，你講果有薪病假係指4/5, 即指連續5日有醫生證明可以 claim 到4日工資，但你呢種1,2日既 sl 係乜都無，唔理你 ft or pt 都一樣"}]}